    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_533316">By that definition, <b><u>absolutely</u></b>; what I'm not for is the removal of guns from society either step by step or wholesale, repealing of the second amendment, etc. I want the government to require licensing for firearms for the same reasons I want the government to require licensing for driving on public roadways: the massive amount of responsibility that comes with such a privilege. Not to mention keeping guns out of the hands of criminals, the clinically insane, etc.<br />
<br />
Wait - did an argument on the internet just end? Is this possible?</div>
