    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_533348">The correct question is why did this guy do this, not with what or how.  There will always be crazy people that snap and do horrible things, that cannot be stopped.  What can be done is to fix our social safety nets so less of them fall through the holes.<br />
<br />
Gun control will never work in the US, gun ownership is to ingrained in the culture. The pioneer, hunter, and cowboy heritage all relied on them.  Background checks and other methods to make sure those purchasing them are not crazy or criminal seems to be the most effective.. if they actually made the process better.</div>
    <!-- / message -->
    
    
