    <td width="30" align="center" valign="middle"><img src="/forums/images/closeq.gif" width="30" height="30" align="right"></td>
  </tr>
</table>
</div>That one the man with the concealed weapon didn't fire his weapon.  It sounded like he had training as well but that's just based on how he told the story and how the news reported it.</div>
