    <div align="left" id="post_message_533374">It isn't sold next to soda and toilet paper at any wal-mart I ever saw... it's sold next to the camping gear, and the bows and arrows, and other hunting supplies. As such, it is well placed. The wal-mart has to follow the same laws and rules as other gun shops.<br />
